org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabUser

  • public final class GitlabUser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component User. This doesn't support create, update, and delete operations. This supports query for users globally or users within a project. See GitlabUser.Query and GitlabUser.ProjectQuery.

    Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/users.html

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  GitlabUser.ProjectQuery
      This extends GitlabQuery and supports query users within a GitlabProject.
      static class  GitlabUser.Query
      This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global users.
